{"tid":1400263,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[硬件撚]討論硬件知識、砌機LIST、解答問題集中帖(182) 望下#1 先","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:23:39.000Z","uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a42e3eb4326a87cfe2032360029ee53d03044c7","tid":1400263,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新人求List需知</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">買前好問問 買後問懵撚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n為方便連登眾巴絲可以幫助你，請你合作<br />\n不但可以令連登眾巴絲可以盡快回覆你的問題，更可以令條List更適合你所需<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">關於所有店舖事項請巴打從其他有效方式聯絡 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">顯卡係蝗語，請講顯示卡或display card </span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9Li1671.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Li1671.gif&h=e2849c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Budget<br />\nNO MONEY NO TALK ，預算上限寬鬆可以買好一點，預算太低可能要將就或繼續儲錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFQCM1P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFQCM1P.gif&h=c0d97530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦主要用途<br />\n你想玩咩遊戲? (多數砌機都會打機，如果唔係請另外講明)<br />\n最好講game名，唔好一句Steam game/blizzard/EA game就算<br />\n因為成千上萬隻人地唔知你玩邊隻<br />\n需唔需要直播或錄製遊戲影片?<br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n玩以上遊戲你最低可接受嘅畫質(Ultra/高/中/低)?最低可接受幾fps?<br />\n如果你預計會玩新遊戲，想幾耐唔駛升級電腦硬件?<br />\n想唔想超頻?散熱需求如何?使唔使靜過Dyson?<br />\n有冇特定嘅牌子信仰?想唔想有華麗嘅RGB光效?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打機 Intel<br />\n多工 文書 AMD</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 現在或將會使用mon的類型<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解像度</span>有分1080p, 2K(1440p), 4K(2160p)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">更新頻率</span>有分60Hz, 144Hz, 240Hz<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">畫面比例</span>有分 16:9, 21:9, 32:9<br />\n你想要咩解像度(畫質)同更新頻率(流暢度)?<br />\n解像度高，會對打機效能造成影響，但畫質會更好<br />\n更新頻率高，如效能足夠可以造成比低更新頻率更好嘅流暢度<br />\n<br />\n5. 自己都學習一些<br />\n講真，班巴絲好憎伸手黨，所以建議你行多一兩步<br />\n哪怕你直接照抄悠二伏List放上黎問，佢地都會出手幫助<br />\n<a href=\"http://yujihw.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com%2F&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=8481317f\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com/</a><br />\n只係Ctrl-C和Ctrl-V咁簡單，大家都會開心嘅事點解唔做呢?<br />\n甚至可能你在過程中已經搵到需要的答案都不一定!<br />\n(砌機list 用作參考 價錢間間唔同自行格價 亦可留意實體店鋪 以下網址用方便砌list之用)<br />\n飛馬:<a href=\"https://shop.pegasushk.net/customize-pc/?MTE3MTg=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.pegasushk.net%2Fcustomize-pc%2F%3FMTE3MTg%3D&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=772a1198\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.pegasushk.net/customize-pc/?MTE3MTg=</a><br />\n法奧:<a href=\"https://www.faroll.com/customize\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faroll.com%2Fcustomize&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=7afc2004\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.faroll.com/customize</a><br />\n終端:<a href=\"https://www.terminalhk.com/pcSystem/customize/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.terminalhk.com%2FpcSystem%2Fcustomize%2F&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b0554186\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.terminalhk.com/pcSystem/customize/</a><br />\nJumbo:<a href=\"http://www.jumbo-computer.com/pricelist.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jumbo-computer.com%2Fpricelist.aspx&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=34299c7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jumbo-computer.com/pricelist.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n6.  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>大腦</del>Google係一樣很有用的東西</span></span><br />\n<br />\n7. 火牛： 平 Antec eco2, delta 500W(Comdex有賣)  貴 corsair RMx OR Evga G2/P2/T2 (G3 有人話QC 有問題 唔推)<br />\nPSU DB: <a href=\"http://www.orionpsudb.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orionpsudb.com%2F&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=357d712a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orionpsudb.com/</a> <br />\n<br />\n8. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請上銅柱(MB and M.2),重覆檢查插好power,hdd led pin,HD AUDIO,MB 24PIN,usb2.0/3.0,fan pin(cpu,cha) or 3pin 4pin</span></span><br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有走好線先</span>）<br />\n<br />\n9. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召喚硬件傳心師</span></span><br />\n冇人知你部機咩spec 呀<br />\n你有咩壞野問題唔該貼返full spec<br />\nCPU, MB, RAM, DISPLAY CARD, PSU etc.<br />\n如果開唔到機請附上機箱內部圖片一張<br />\n<br />\n10.<br />\n邊到買野好？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HppkYop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHppkYop.jpg&h=a09ec374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 3C1J</span></strong><br />\n黃金：中央田 CentralField<br />\n黃金：正都 Capital<br />\n黃金：匯訊 Comdex<br />\n旺電：珍寶 Jumbo<br />\n<br />\n網店：<br />\n法奧 Faroll <br />\n香港終端 hkterminal<br />\n飛馬 Pegasus<br />\n<br />\n海外：<br />\n新蛋 NewEgg<br />\n美馬 Amazon<br />\n<br />\n11.<br />\nAMD 拆cpu cooler 前記得整熱部機<br />\nAmd 拔劍有事幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12.<br />\nH310 A320 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係冇budget 先考慮<br />\nCooler Master 不是好東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見親都係叫你轉嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n13. 買咩箱好 <br />\n500樓下:<br />\nATX: Antec P7/8, DeepCool MATREXX 55 <br />\nMATX:  Antec P6, CM NR400<br />\nITX: Sharkon C10 <br />\n<br />\n1000樓下:<br />\nATX: FD Define C,Antec P110<br />\nMATX: FD Define Mini C<br />\nITX: FD Node 304/ Node 202, NZXT H200, SilverStone RVZ 01/02/03, Evolv ITX <br />\n<br />\n1000樓上:<br />\nATX: FD Define R6, Phanteks P600S, lian-li O11 dynamic, Corsair 680X<br />\nMATX: Corsair 280X<br />\nITX: Inwin A1plus(包火牛)<br />\n<br />\n文書 Deskmini (Build in Motherboard, PSU) <span style=\"color: red;\">RAM(NB),CPU,2.5 HDD/SSD, PCIE M.2 SSD 自己買</span><br />\nIntel: 310<br />\nAMD: A300<br />\n<br />\n14. 檢測效能方法 - Afterburner(AB) + Rivatuner Statistics Server(RTSS)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">AB為GPU OC software <strong>咩牌子</strong>都用得<br />\n配合埋RTSS 就可以實現OSD 功能</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">有咩用? 如果你發現打機果時lag 或者想知部機依家效能有冇問題<br />\n利用AB + RTSS 就可以即時check 到哂CPU GPU usage 同 tempature. <br />\nEG: CPU/GPU過熱降頻 係咪要改善機箱風道?<br />\nCPU 長期100% 代表粒u 唔夠力</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msi.com/page/afterburner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msi.com%2Fpage%2Fafterburner&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=4a7460ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msi.com/page/afterburner</a><br />\n<br />\n15. Uninstall GPU driver: 換任何卡請DDU 一次<br />\nDDU<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guru3d.com/files-details/display-driver-uninstaller-download.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guru3d.com%2Ffiles-details%2Fdisplay-driver-uninstaller-download.html&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0277e98d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.guru3d.com/files-details/display-driver-uninstaller-download.html</a><br />\n<br />\n16. For Advance Information<br />\nvrm 資料<br />\namd : <a href=\"https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/pga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hardwareluxx.de%2Fcommunity%2Ff12%2Fpga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=1f9c1a13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/pga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html</a><br />\nintel : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/lga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hardwareluxx.de%2Fcommunity%2Ff12%2Flga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=6453e8ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/lga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html</a><br />\nSata / NVME SSD 網上資料 (含Controller, DRAM, NAND Chip Brand資料)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1B27_j9NDPU3cNlj2HKcrfpJKHkOf-Oi1DbuuQva2gT4/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1B27_j9NDPU3cNlj2HKcrfpJKHkOf-Oi1DbuuQva2gT4%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0de15206\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1B27_j9NDPU3cNlj2HKcrfpJKHkOf-Oi1DbuuQva2gT4/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n17. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>茶包走線<br />\n茶包裝X62</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n有咩要加再同1001講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好亂咁改1001 呀 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9403af0989cabb02679732ab0ac14267bc4fc246","tid":1400263,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80410085b643dded2d795ac45a55d5dac3da7c4d","tid":1400263,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n買完HT返黎睇膠list"},{"pid":"5f46a298c7829311a3fdb3fb9619554bc0c1c630","tid":1400263,"uid":83840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"咩叫茶包裝x62<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}